    {
        "user": "UJBAJNFLK",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1778659076.297409",
        "client_msg_id": "fc9d2c02-6ee7-44eb-8500-89712062cfee",
        "text": "In a VC-funded world, we are likely to see backup-as-a-service, but not personal data ownership. Of course, backup-as-a-service is preferable to the current situation as long as the backup service is independent of the PDS hosting service AND this independence is transparent to users and guaranteed to persist. Which, unfortunately, is unlikely in a VC-funded world.",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "e169f54bbaf8",
            "image_72": "https:\/\/avatars.slack-edge.com\/2021-03-12\/1859691333940_e169f54bbaf8b9b36b12_72.png",
            "first_name": "Konrad",
            "real_name": "Konrad Hinsen",
            "display_name": "Konrad Hinsen",
            "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
            "name": "konrad.hinsen",
            "is_restricted": false,
            "is_ultra_restricted": false
        },
        "thread_ts": "1778473180.151529",
        "parent_user_id": "U02E4DAQGSZ",
        "blocks": [
            {
                "type": "rich_text",
                "block_id": "xfybD",
                "elements": [
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "In a VC-funded world, we are likely to see backup-as-a-service, but not personal data ownership. Of course, backup-as-a-service is preferable to the current situation as long as the backup service is independent of the PDS hosting service AND this independence is transparent to users and guaranteed to persist. Which, unfortunately, is unlikely in a VC-funded world."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "user": "UJBAJNFLK",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1778659408.011069",
        "client_msg_id": "0ae46b30-4511-459b-b63b-72c38f76f70c",
        "text": "Great examples. Which can be seen as special cases of the general phenomenon that I expect to happen: less collaboration and consensus-seeking between humans, replaced by more dependence on LLM-mediated services for working around tech incompatibilities (and human ones - think of machine translation).\n\nThis might well be an acceptable trade-off in a world in which LLMs are economically accessible to everyone and a diverse LLM market ensures that no single party can inject biases into LLM-based mediation. Which is unfortunately not our current world.",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "e169f54bbaf8",
            "image_72": "https:\/\/avatars.slack-edge.com\/2021-03-12\/1859691333940_e169f54bbaf8b9b36b12_72.png",
            "first_name": "Konrad",
            "real_name": "Konrad Hinsen",
